            "text": "ROOT",
            "relation": "null"
        },
        {
            "id": 1,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "The Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome - Coronavirus ( SARS - CoV ) 3a locus encodes a 274 a.a . novel protein ,",
            "relation": "BACKGROUND"
        },
        {
            "id": 2,
            "parent": 1,
            "text": "and its expression has been confirmed in SARS patients . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 3,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "To study functional roles of 3a ,",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 4,
            "parent": 0,
            "text": "we established a transgenic fly model for the SARS - CoV 3a gene . <S>",
            "relation": "ROOT"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "Misexpression of 3a in Drosophila caused a dominant rough eye phenotype . <S>",
            "relation": "FINDINGS"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "parent": 7,
            "text": "Using a specific monoclonal antibody ,",
            "relation": "MANNER-MEANS"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "parent": 8,
            "text": "we demonstrated",
            "relation": "ATTRIBUTION"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "parent": 5,
            "text": "that the 3a protein displayed a punctate cytoplasmic localization in Drosophila as in SARS - CoV - infected cells . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "parent": 8,
            "text": "We provide genetic evidence",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "parent": 11,
            "text": "to support",
            "relation": "ATTRIBUTION"
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "that 3a is functionally related to clathrin - mediated endocytosis . <S>",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "parent": 13,
            "text": "We further found",
            "relation": "ATTRIBUTION"
        },
        {
            "id": 13,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "that 3a misexpression induces apoptosis ,",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 14,
            "parent": 13,
            "text": "which could be modulated by cellular cytochrome c levels and caspase activity . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 15,
            "parent": 13,
            "text": "From a forward genetic screen , 78 dominant 3a modifying loci were recovered",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 16,
            "parent": 17,
            "text": "and the identity of these modifiers revealed",
            "relation": "ATTRIBUTION"
        },
        {
            "id": 17,
            "parent": 15,
            "text": "that the severity of the 3a - induced rough eye phenotype depends on multiple cellular processes",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 18,
            "parent": 17,
            "text": "including gene transcriptional regulation . <S> <P>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        }
    ]
}